###
# Lessons - Public lesson detail
GET {{host}}/api/lessons/{{lessonId}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

###
# Lessons - Admin update lesson
PUT {{host}}/api/courses/{{courseId}}/lessons/{{lessonId}}
Authorization: {{authorization}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Authentication with JWT - Updated",
  "summary": "Updated lesson summary.",
  "orderIndex": 1,
  "isPublished": true,
  "contentBlocks": [
    {
      "orderIndex": 1,
      "type": "Text",
      "content": "JWT enables stateless auth for APIs.",
